==English==
===Noun===
'''transacetylase'''
#{{biochemistry}} any [[enzyme]] that [[catalyze]]s the [[transfer]] of an [[acetyl]] [[group]] from one [[molecule]] to another.  It is produced by the 'a' structural gene of the [[lac operon]].

===Synonyms===
*[[acetyltransferase]]
